I have to turn myself in.

15:09.078 --> 15:11.831
Whoa, murderer.
Don't you think that's a little selfish?

15:11.997 --> 15:15.626
- What would your family do?
- But I killed my friend.

15:15.793 --> 15:18.128
How can I live with myself?

15:18.295 --> 15:22.215
Don't worry, honey. I'll help you put
this horrible business behind you.

15:24.259 --> 15:26.427
Trust me, honey. This is the best way.

15:26.594 --> 15:30.974
We have to destroy the body
so you won't be implicated.

15:31.140 --> 15:34.644
There. Now you have closure
and our grass will be green all winter.

15:38.230 --> 15:40.399
- Hey, hey, hey.
- Where's your nose, Kevin?

15:40.566 --> 15:43.443
Shouldn't you be out raping
the star-struck masses with it?

15:43.610 --> 15:46.363
Nose? What are you...?
Oh, oh, that. Yeah, yeah.

15:46.530 --> 15:50.908
Look, I really owe you guys an apology.
I lost sight of what's important.

15:51.075 --> 15:55.746
It's not what you have right here,
it's what you have right here.

15:56.956 --> 15:59.750
- That's where my heart is.
- You were a real jerk, Roger.

15:59.917 --> 16:04.629
Guilty. And the worst part is,
it almost cost me my friends.

16:04.796 --> 16:06.798
Hugs?

16:06.965 --> 16:11.011
In celebrity news, Kevin Bacon
was involved in a hit-and-run accident...

16:11.177 --> 16:13.555
...right here in Langley Falls.
- What?

16:13.722 --> 16:16.474
The whole incident was captured
by a nearby traffic cam.

16:32.739 --> 16:36.868
Bacon fled and was arrested 20 minutes
later, across the country, in Hollywood.

16:37.035 --> 16:41.664
I didn't think I did it,
but it's clearly me on the tape.

16:42.582 --> 16:43.666
Roger.

16:43.833 --> 16:47.669
I'm gonna turn this cheese sandwich
into a panini.

16:53.050 --> 16:58.554
I'm leaving, Stan. I killed someone
and it's tearing my soul apart.

16:58.721 --> 17:00.681
If I can't turn myself in...

17:00.848 --> 17:03.934
...then I've gotta dedicate my life
to helping others.

17:04.101 --> 17:07.188
I'm going to India to care for the poor.

17:07.355 --> 17:10.066
- Tell the children I love them.
- Wait, Francine.

17:10.232 --> 17:12.192
You're not the monster
you think you are.

17:12.358 --> 17:13.777
Of course I am.

17:13.943 --> 17:17.864
I've gone over that whole terrible night
two times in my head...

17:18.031 --> 17:22.242
...and the only other explanation is
that someone's framing me.

17:22.410 --> 17:26.288
But who would do something
so awful?

17:28.415 --> 17:31.585
There's six months worth of casseroles
in the freezer.

17:31.752 --> 17:34.129
I love you.

17:38.092 --> 17:40.134
- I really miss Mom.
- Me too.

17:40.301 --> 17:42.595
I don't miss her six-month supply
of casseroles.

17:42.762 --> 17:44.722
Man, I'm glad we finally finished them.

17:44.889 --> 17:48.518
I wish Dad hadn't added those noodles
to make them last twice as long.

17:48.684 --> 17:51.771
What choice did he have?
Freezer burn ruined 90 percent of them.

17:51.938 --> 17:56.358
Wait, wait, wait a minute.
I can do this. Six divided by...

17:56.525 --> 17:58.318
Carry the noodle...

17:58.485 --> 18:00.153
